Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/Parashare Blood Curdling Scream Edition

Dave digs deep this week to uncover stories from around the world. The Israelis know Aliens exist, Ghosts are Screaming, Iowans encounter Sasquatch and The Zodiac mocks us from the grave.

All that PLUS your real life encounters with the Supernatural.
